headline: Viatris’ Work To Advance Access and Public Health
summary: NORTHAMPTON, MA / ACCESS Newswire / October 7, 2025 / In 2024, Viatris provided medicines addressing the top 10 of the WHO's leading causes of death globally. We have taken a deliberate approach to expand access to our wide portfolio across geographies ...
